computer/Scid_366_released_chess_database_179456.html\">Scid 3.6.6 released (chess database)</a> by <a href=\"/Pascal_Georges\" title=\"Pascal Georges\">Pascal Georges</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.avlerchess.com/\">Avler Chess</a>, March 07, 2007</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=13095\">Scid 3.6.11 released</a> by <a href=\"/Pascal_Georges\" title=\"Pascal Georges\">Pascal Georges</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 13, 2007</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=13412\">Scid 3.6.13 released</a> by <a href=\"/Pascal_Georges\" title=\"Pascal Georges\">Pascal Georges</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 26, 2007</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=13638\">Scid 3.6.14 released</a> by <a href=\"/Pascal_Georges\" title=\"Pascal Georges\">Pascal Georges</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 08, 2007</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=14604\">Scid for Pocket PC - First Beta released</a> by <a href=\"/Pascal_Georges\" title=\"Pascal Georges\">Pascal Georges</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 21, 2007</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/rec.games.chess.computer/I-J53bggxm8/YJGioTFWSHUJ\">Why Scid should stay alive [Re: Statistical significance of score differences - new release ofChessDB]</a> by <a href=\"/Pascal_Georges\" title=\"Pascal Georges\">Pascal Georges</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, August 22, 2007</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/rec.games.chess.computer/aaziPZO-1mo/Jwr-RN2HOBsJ\">FAKE Scid released (chess database sof